title: range errors in cdfs sometimes disappear when the xrange is restricted
pid: bdb00fc4-4329-411e-9644-6f4f15c37c6b
body: |2-
  draw.single_cdf( x[ x<10 ], # PITFALL : not restricting x here => a range error
                   "cdf of (spending / income) across income-earning households"
                   , xmin = 0, xmax = 8
                 )
